reviewText: This movie is amazing! Almost exact to the story found in the Bible and my kids love it!
I regret buying it, and we have other NEST DVDs which are great like The Kingdom of Heaven and the Animated Passion.

This is another Nest Entertainment production of an Old Testament character and they have done an excellent job, true to Scripture. They are very well made and the animation is very good. I am pleased with all that I have purchased.
It bridged a lot of gaps on Elijah for our kids in class.  I'm glad we bought it.  Will buy more like it.
